			description: [
				"Here is the default method of converting &cRedstone Dust&r into &0Flux&r."
				""
				"&bStep 1:&r Find some &5Bedrock&r."
				""
				"&bStep 2:&r Place some &dObsidian&r above it, leaving one block space in between."
				""
				"&bStep 3:&r Throw some &cRedstone Dust&r in the gap left by the &5Bedrock&r and &dObsidian&r."
				""
				"&bStep 4:&r &aLeft-click&r the &dObsidian&r. The &dObsidian&r will crush the &cRedstone Dust&r against the &5Bedrock&r and create &0Flux&r!"
				""
				"There is &nno limit&r to the amount of &cRedstone Dust&r you can use each time."
