			description: [
				"&eFlux Configurator&r can be used to &o&baccess&r, &o&bedit&r, &o&bdelete&r networks on the go, and shares the same &o&bGUI&r as connectors."
				""
				"&eFlux Configurator&r can also be used to &9copy&r/&cpaste&r settings &o&bbetween connectors&r."
				""
				"&bCopying Settings:&r"
				"&aShift+Right-click&r on a connector to copy it's settings and then &aRight-click&r on a connector you wish to paste the settings to. If you &aRight-click&r something which isn't a connector you'll bring up the &dNetwork&r &o&bGUI&r and also you'll be able to edit the settings which the &2Configurator&r will paste."
